1
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:55,000
"Lost To You"

2
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:57,700
(Episode 7)

3
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:03,199
Secrets are like glass.

4
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:04,999
Once shattered,

5
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:07,799
they don't just cut the one hiding them,

6
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:11,800
but also anyone who tries to offer warmth.

7
00:01:17,083 --> 00:01:19,041
Your dad asked me to check on you.

8
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:21,920
He's worried you'll run
wild in this small town,

9
00:01:23,083 --> 00:01:25,723
and even more worried you'll get
too close to your second brother.

10
00:01:26,041 --> 00:01:27,561
He's keeping a really close eye on me.

11
00:01:28,875 --> 00:01:29,958
Afraid that I'm gay too,

12
00:01:31,041 --> 00:01:32,226
and will bring shame to the Zhan family.

13
00:01:32,250 --> 00:01:33,000
Zhan Wang.

14
00:01:33,208 --> 00:01:34,208
Don't say that.

15
00:01:34,791 --> 00:01:36,391
Your dad only wants what's best for you.

16
00:01:36,916 --> 00:01:38,601
Our families have been
close for generations.

17
00:01:38,625 --> 00:01:39,708
Our marriage

18
00:01:40,416 --> 00:01:41,416
was arranged long ago.

19
00:01:41,875 --> 00:01:42,875
That was their decision.

20
00:01:44,041 --> 00:01:45,041
I never agreed to it.

21
00:01:45,500 --> 00:01:46,958
But you never objected either,

22
00:01:47,166 --> 00:01:48,166
did you?

23
00:01:48,416 --> 00:01:49,708
Ever since we were kids,

24
00:01:49,916 --> 00:01:52,000
everyone thought we'd end up together.

25
00:01:53,416 --> 00:01:54,458
A perfect match,

26
00:01:54,583 --> 00:01:55,791
childhood sweethearts.

27
00:01:56,166 --> 00:01:57,166
What a beautiful story.

28
00:02:05,750 --> 00:02:07,125
Your drawing skills have improved.

29
00:02:10,291 --> 00:02:12,125
Especially these eyes.

30
00:02:13,208 --> 00:02:15,750
You put a lot of heart into drawing him.

31
00:02:16,375 --> 00:02:17,375
Lin Xia.

32
00:02:18,166 --> 00:02:19,250
I'm just curious.

33
00:02:19,833 --> 00:02:21,125
What's really going on

34
00:02:21,958 --> 00:02:23,125
between you and Xu Yuan?

35
00:02:25,541 --> 00:02:26,541
None of your business.

36
00:02:28,041 --> 00:02:29,241
I'm staying in the guest room.

37
00:02:31,083 --> 00:02:32,083
How long are you staying?

38
00:02:32,333 --> 00:02:34,041
Depends on my mood.

39
00:02:53,500 --> 00:02:54,166
Xu Yuan.

40
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:55,125
You're here.

41
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:56,740
I'm staying here this week too.

42
00:02:57,083 --> 00:02:58,142
So I might have to trouble you

43
00:02:58,166 --> 00:02:59,458
to tutor me as well.

44
00:03:00,833 --> 00:03:01,833
Sure.

45
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:04,083
Zhan Wang's friends are my friends.

46
00:03:04,416 --> 00:03:05,416
Come on in.

47
00:03:12,375 --> 00:03:13,458
Xu Yuan, sit over there.

48
00:03:15,291 --> 00:03:16,291
Xu Yuan,

49
00:03:18,583 --> 00:03:19,583
why are you sitting here?

50
00:03:19,833 --> 00:03:20,833
Come over here.

51
00:03:25,708 --> 00:03:26,166
Lin Xia,

52
00:03:26,416 --> 00:03:27,416
go sit over there.

53
00:03:28,041 --> 00:03:29,041
Hurry up.

54
00:03:29,875 --> 00:03:30,291
Fine.

55
00:03:30,375 --> 00:03:31,392
You guys do your tutoring.

56
00:03:31,416 --> 00:03:32,083
I'll do my drawing.

57
00:03:32,416 --> 00:03:33,416
Pretend like I'm not here.

58
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:46,500
For this problem,

59
00:03:46,666 --> 00:03:48,041
if t equals the square root of x,

60
00:03:48,333 --> 00:03:50,375
then x equals t squared.

61
00:03:53,083 --> 00:03:54,083
Wait.

62
00:03:54,125 --> 00:03:55,708
Why set it up like that?

63
00:03:56,208 --> 00:03:57,608
You fell asleep in class yesterday,

64
00:03:58,291 --> 00:03:59,291
so you missed this part.

65
00:04:00,916 --> 00:04:01,916
Zhan Wang,

66
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,720
you wouldn't get it even if you were awake.

67
00:04:04,250 --> 00:04:09,208
You used to need me to draw diagrams and
explain trigonometric functions over and over.

68
00:04:09,416 --> 00:04:10,750
Why bring up middle school?

69
00:04:11,208 --> 00:04:11,825
Yuan,

70
00:04:12,083 --> 00:04:13,083
let's continue.

71
00:04:15,250 --> 00:04:16,892
I have some things to
take care of at home today.

72
00:04:16,916 --> 00:04:17,956
I need to head back early.

73
00:04:18,541 --> 00:04:19,541
But you just started.

74
00:04:20,375 --> 00:04:21,958
Didn't we agree to finish this chapter?

75
00:04:24,083 --> 00:04:25,323
The concepts are pretty simple.

76
00:04:26,083 --> 00:04:27,083
Or,

77
00:04:29,166 --> 00:04:30,625
you can have Lin Xia help you.

78
00:04:32,125 --> 00:04:33,125
Sure.

79
00:04:33,916 --> 00:04:36,875
My science grades aren't
as good as Xu Yuan's,

80
00:04:37,750 --> 00:04:39,875
but I can still manage

81
00:04:40,041 --> 00:04:41,361
to tutor an idiot like Zhan Wang.

82
00:04:41,916 --> 00:04:42,916
Did you forget?

83
00:04:42,958 --> 00:04:44,476
Before the final exams in sophomore year,

84
00:04:44,500 --> 00:04:46,791
who tutored you in math at your place,

85
00:04:47,125 --> 00:04:49,485
and we ended up falling asleep
on the study floor together?

86
00:04:50,291 --> 00:04:51,291
Lin Xia.

87
00:04:51,666 --> 00:04:52,666
Am I wrong?

88
00:04:52,958 --> 00:04:54,000
It's the truth.

89
00:04:55,250 --> 00:04:57,208
Don't you agree, Xu Yuan?

90
00:04:58,125 --> 00:04:59,165
To teach someone like him,

91
00:04:59,416 --> 00:05:01,833
you need patience to keep him in line.

92
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:04,458
Otherwise, he'll sneak out to
play basketball in a heartbeat.

93
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,760
I'll leave you two to
talk. I'm heading out.

94
00:05:07,291 --> 00:05:08,291
Wait, I'll walk you out.

95
00:05:09,708 --> 00:05:10,708
No need.

96
00:05:12,208 --> 00:05:13,208
It's late,

97
00:05:13,291 --> 00:05:14,451
and the coastal road is dark.

98
00:05:15,916 --> 00:05:17,333
Lin Xia is waiting to tutor you.

99
00:05:18,250 --> 00:05:19,250
Don't keep her waiting.

100
00:05:20,416 --> 00:05:21,416
Zhan Wang,

101
00:05:21,500 --> 00:05:22,625
why are you so nervous?

102
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:24,500
Don't tell me

103
00:05:25,208 --> 00:05:26,968
you're really just like
your second brother...?

104
00:05:27,375 --> 00:05:28,375
Our family matters

105
00:05:28,750 --> 00:05:29,750
are none of your concern.

106
00:05:30,208 --> 00:05:31,250
I'm just warning you,

107
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,000
Zhan Wang.

108
00:05:33,416 --> 00:05:35,536
Once you take certain
paths, there's no turning back.

109
00:05:38,791 --> 00:05:40,166
Your dad will never allow it.

110
00:05:41,208 --> 00:05:43,368
Just think about what
happened to your second brother.

111
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,000
Xu Yuan!

112
00:06:18,083 --> 00:06:18,625
Xu Yuan!

113
00:06:19,041 --> 00:06:20,517
Hurry to the rooftop of the art building.

114
00:06:20,541 --> 00:06:21,941
Zhan Wang and Lin Xia are up there.

115
00:06:22,416 --> 00:06:24,767
When I was coming back from
the art room with the homework,

116
00:06:24,791 --> 00:06:26,083
I heard some noise upstairs.

117
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:27,892
It sounded like Lin Xia was crying.

118
00:06:27,916 --> 00:06:28,791
She was definitely crying.

119
00:06:28,916 --> 00:06:30,596
It was quiet, but I could hear it clearly.

120
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:31,875
Zhan Wang was speaking too,

121
00:06:32,125 --> 00:06:33,125
and he sounded really,

122
00:06:33,583 --> 00:06:34,708
really harsh.

123
00:06:35,083 --> 00:06:36,000
Go check on them.

124
00:06:36,083 --> 00:06:37,083
Are they fighting?

125
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:39,083
I heard Lin Xia is Zhan Wang's fiancée.

126
00:06:39,208 --> 00:06:41,288
Are they calling off the
engagement and breaking up?

127
00:06:41,791 --> 00:06:43,151
I really think something is wrong.

128
00:06:43,666 --> 00:06:45,375
Lin Xia is usually such a gentle person.

129
00:06:45,666 --> 00:06:47,875
And with Zhan Wang's temper,

130
00:06:48,833 --> 00:06:50,017
I'm worried something might happen.

131
00:06:50,041 --> 00:06:51,291
Go check on them, Xu Yuan.

132
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:52,583
Hurry!

133
00:06:55,666 --> 00:06:56,166
Wait,

134
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:57,820
why are you asking Xu Yuan to go?

135
00:06:57,916 --> 00:06:59,556
Won't that make things even more awkward?

136
00:06:59,875 --> 00:07:00,375
Why?

137
00:07:00,708 --> 00:07:01,708
Are you stupid?

138
00:07:03,083 --> 00:07:03,625
Go check on them.

139
00:07:03,750 --> 00:07:04,291
Make sure nothing bad happens.

140
00:07:04,416 --> 00:07:05,166
Let's go, let's go.

141
00:07:05,166 --> 00:07:06,166
Hurry, let's go!

142
00:07:07,083 --> 00:07:07,583
Lin Xia,

143
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,333
what we had is in the past.

144
00:07:10,041 --> 00:07:11,041
Is it really in the past?

145
00:07:12,458 --> 00:07:13,750
If my brother were still alive,

146
00:07:14,416 --> 00:07:15,416
I'd want to ask him

147
00:07:15,958 --> 00:07:18,398
if dying in the mountains for
someone like that was worth it.

148
00:07:24,208 --> 00:07:25,208
Excuse me.

149
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:26,750
Excuse me.

150
00:07:28,416 --> 00:07:29,416
Are you guys...

151
00:07:29,708 --> 00:07:30,708
Are you guys okay?

152
00:07:34,666 --> 00:07:35,250
We're fine.

153
00:07:35,375 --> 00:07:36,375
Why did you come up here?

154
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:37,166
It's nothing.

155
00:07:37,458 --> 00:07:38,958
We were just talking about the past.

156
00:07:46,208 --> 00:07:47,208
If it's because of me

157
00:07:47,875 --> 00:07:48,500
that you two are...

158
00:07:48,625 --> 00:07:49,625
It's not your fault.

159
00:07:51,541 --> 00:07:52,541
It's just that I...

160
00:07:53,583 --> 00:07:55,333
I just thought of some sad things.

161
00:07:58,250 --> 00:07:59,250
I just don't want

162
00:08:02,416 --> 00:08:04,096
the people I care about to get hurt again.

163
00:08:10,208 --> 00:08:11,208
Lin Xia!

164
00:08:12,416 --> 00:08:13,416
I...

165
00:08:13,458 --> 00:08:15,338
I was just trying to keep
you from getting hit.

166
00:08:16,041 --> 00:08:17,041
What's going on?

167
00:08:17,083 --> 00:08:18,000
Are they fighting?

168
00:08:18,083 --> 00:08:18,750
Stop talking and help!

169
00:08:18,833 --> 00:08:19,500
Go on, help them!

170
00:08:19,541 --> 00:08:20,125
Xu Yuan pushed her.

171
00:08:20,208 --> 00:08:21,208
Probably out of jealousy.

172
00:08:21,625 --> 00:08:22,916
A jinx is always a jinx.

173
00:08:23,083 --> 00:08:24,083
The Jinx is acting up.

174
00:08:24,125 --> 00:08:25,765
Her hand is hurt. Let's go to the clinic.

175
00:08:25,875 --> 00:08:26,375
Lin Xia,

176
00:08:26,833 --> 00:08:27,416
are you okay?

177
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:28,750
Here,

178
00:08:29,375 --> 00:08:30,375
careful.

179
00:08:31,916 --> 00:08:32,916
Careful.

180
00:08:33,125 --> 00:08:33,625
What are you looking at?

181
00:08:34,041 --> 00:08:35,041
Move!

182
00:08:39,250 --> 00:08:40,559
Lin Xia is applying to the art academy.

183
00:08:40,583 --> 00:08:41,976
If her hand is ruined, she's done for.

184
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,000
Exactly.

185
00:08:50,333 --> 00:08:51,333
It hurts so much.

186
00:08:52,791 --> 00:08:53,291
Hang in there.

187
00:08:53,541 --> 00:08:54,981
The school doctor will be here soon.

188
00:08:55,833 --> 00:08:56,833
What happened?

189
00:08:58,083 --> 00:08:59,083
Let me take a look.

190
00:09:07,250 --> 00:09:08,333
It's you.

191
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:11,500
Long time no see,

192
00:09:11,926 --> 00:09:12,926
Xia-xia.

193
00:09:13,833 --> 00:09:14,833
Don't touch me.

194
00:09:19,944 --> 00:09:20,984
You need to bind it.

195
00:09:21,125 --> 00:09:22,685
It looks like a distal radius fracture.

196
00:09:22,916 --> 00:09:24,809
Go to the nearest hospital
for an X-ray right away.

197
00:09:24,833 --> 00:09:26,309
Why are you acting like a good person now?

198
00:09:26,333 --> 00:09:27,333
Zhan Xu,

199
00:09:28,041 --> 00:09:29,750
stop playing the angel in white.

200
00:09:34,375 --> 00:09:35,583
Do you know who he is?

201
00:09:36,666 --> 00:09:38,946
He's Zhan Xu, the second
young master of the Zhan family.

202
00:09:39,833 --> 00:09:41,666
He's gay. He likes men.

203
00:09:42,958 --> 00:09:43,958
Seriously?

204
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,625
No wonder he's always been single.

205
00:09:47,083 --> 00:09:48,083
That's disgusting.

206
00:09:49,750 --> 00:09:51,950
He convinced my brother to
run away with him back then.

207
00:09:52,208 --> 00:09:53,291
Now he's hiding out here

208
00:09:54,583 --> 00:09:55,666
and seducing students.

209
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:57,208
And him?

210
00:09:57,375 --> 00:09:59,083
Do you know how he lost his hearing?

211
00:09:59,416 --> 00:10:00,666
His dad beat him deaf.

212
00:10:00,916 --> 00:10:02,434
Because he's disgusting.
Because he's filthy.

213
00:10:02,458 --> 00:10:03,458
Enough!

214
00:10:03,708 --> 00:10:04,708
Lin Xia.

215
00:10:05,083 --> 00:10:06,083
Your hand is injured.

216
00:10:06,291 --> 00:10:07,291
Let me treat it first.

217
00:10:07,583 --> 00:10:08,750
Am I wrong?

218
00:10:10,208 --> 00:10:11,208
Zhan Xu!

219
00:10:11,958 --> 00:10:13,458
Do you dare deny that you like men?

220
00:10:15,625 --> 00:10:17,583
Do you dare deny that
you stole my brother away?

221
00:10:17,750 --> 00:10:18,870
And then you got him killed!

222
00:10:20,583 --> 00:10:21,250
What about Bian Ye?

223
00:10:21,541 --> 00:10:22,541
Exactly.

224
00:10:39,291 --> 00:10:40,291
Lin Xia.

225
00:10:41,166 --> 00:10:42,166
You hate me.

226
00:10:42,250 --> 00:10:43,250
I know that.

227
00:10:44,291 --> 00:10:45,309
But no matter how much you hate me,

228
00:10:45,333 --> 00:10:46,833
your hand is what matters right now.

229
00:10:48,583 --> 00:10:49,583
Hold her still.

230
00:10:49,666 --> 00:10:51,266
I need to put a temporary splint on her.

231
00:10:58,666 --> 00:10:59,666
Don't touch me!

232
00:11:01,166 --> 00:11:02,333
Get away from me!

233
00:11:07,208 --> 00:11:08,928
Take her to the town hospital for an X-ray.

234
00:11:09,250 --> 00:11:10,250
She might need a cast.

235
00:11:11,625 --> 00:11:12,665
Everyone, please leave.

236
00:11:13,125 --> 00:11:14,125
Don't crowd around here.

237
00:11:17,875 --> 00:11:18,875
Let's go.

238
00:11:33,458 --> 00:11:34,458
Are...

239
00:11:35,500 --> 00:11:36,500
Are you okay?

240
00:11:37,541 --> 00:11:38,541
I'm fine.

241
00:11:38,916 --> 00:11:39,916
But you...

242
00:11:40,625 --> 00:11:42,583
We'll have to cancel
today's tutoring session.

243
00:11:42,916 --> 00:11:44,375
Who cares about tutoring right now?

244
00:11:44,666 --> 00:11:45,892
She said all those things
about you in front of everyone.

245
00:11:45,916 --> 00:11:46,708
Are you just going to let it go?

246
00:11:46,916 --> 00:11:47,916
Lin Xia was right.

247
00:11:49,791 --> 00:11:50,916
I am gay.

248
00:11:51,875 --> 00:11:53,235
You already knew that, didn't you?

249
00:12:04,666 --> 00:12:05,666
What are you doing?

250
00:12:06,125 --> 00:12:07,125
Packing up.

251
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:10,000
Why?

252
00:12:15,250 --> 00:12:16,250
Bian Ye,

253
00:12:16,916 --> 00:12:17,958
in a small town like this,

254
00:12:18,333 --> 00:12:19,791
a gay school doctor like me

255
00:12:20,833 --> 00:12:21,833
won't last very long.

256
00:12:27,166 --> 00:12:27,833
Dr. Zhan,

257
00:12:28,083 --> 00:12:29,083
we need to talk.

258
00:12:29,750 --> 00:12:31,041
Young man, please step outside.

259
00:12:41,541 --> 00:12:42,541
Dr. Zhan,

260
00:12:42,833 --> 00:12:45,166
what just happened has caused quite a stir.

261
00:12:45,916 --> 00:12:46,416
You know,

262
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:47,541
our school

263
00:12:47,708 --> 00:12:49,166
is just a small town school.

264
00:12:49,416 --> 00:12:51,500
People here are quite conservative.

265
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,250
And the parents...

266
00:12:54,791 --> 00:12:55,791
I understand,

267
00:12:56,291 --> 00:12:57,291
Principal.

268
00:12:58,250 --> 00:12:59,930
I'm willing to take a temporary suspension

269
00:13:00,125 --> 00:13:01,885
while the school decides
how to handle this.

270
00:13:02,625 --> 00:13:03,291
Dr. Zhan,

271
00:13:03,500 --> 00:13:04,875
you're a good doctor.

272
00:13:05,750 --> 00:13:06,790
But regarding this matter,

273
00:13:06,833 --> 00:13:09,750
we need time to hold a
meeting and discuss it.

274
00:13:10,958 --> 00:13:12,833
Until a decision is made,

275
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:14,750
I'm afraid...

276
00:13:21,833 --> 00:13:22,833
I understand.

277
00:13:23,625 --> 00:13:24,625
Principal,

278
00:13:25,333 --> 00:13:26,573
I'll hand over my duties today.

279
00:13:29,541 --> 00:13:30,541
Why should you?

280
00:13:31,333 --> 00:13:32,375
Just because he likes men,

281
00:13:32,500 --> 00:13:33,660
he can't be a doctor anymore?

282
00:13:33,958 --> 00:13:35,083
He saved someone today!

283
00:13:35,291 --> 00:13:36,291
You saw it yourself!

284
00:13:36,500 --> 00:13:37,767
Does saving lives depend on gender?

285
00:13:37,791 --> 00:13:39,000
Or who you're attracted to?

286
00:13:39,500 --> 00:13:40,500
Young man,

287
00:13:41,375 --> 00:13:43,333
this is an administrative matter.

288
00:13:43,457 --> 00:13:44,832
What fucking
administrative matter?

289
00:13:44,893 --> 00:13:47,058
You're just afraid of gossip
from busybody parents!

290
00:13:47,083 --> 00:13:48,083
Is he a bad doctor?

291
00:13:48,458 --> 00:13:49,778
Has he ever mistreated a patient?

292
00:13:52,166 --> 00:13:53,446
What grade and class are you in?

293
00:13:53,791 --> 00:13:54,951
Who is your homeroom teacher?

294
00:13:55,375 --> 00:13:56,375
Bian Ye,

295
00:13:57,333 --> 00:13:58,333
stop.

296
00:13:59,083 --> 00:14:00,083
Why should I stop?

297
00:14:00,458 --> 00:14:01,625
Is this fair to you?

298
00:14:02,041 --> 00:14:03,809
They didn't care when they
needed you to save lives.

299
00:14:03,833 --> 00:14:05,233
Now they're just tossing you aside!

300
00:14:07,208 --> 00:14:08,208
Bian Ye,

301
00:14:08,541 --> 00:14:09,541
listen to me.

302
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:14,500
Principal,

303
00:14:14,958 --> 00:14:15,958
I'm sorry.

304
00:14:16,250 --> 00:14:17,625
He's just a bit emotional.

305
00:14:18,500 --> 00:14:20,140
It's my fault for not handling this well.

306
00:14:20,500 --> 00:14:21,583
I'll take him out now.

307
00:14:23,958 --> 00:14:24,958
Dr. Zhan,

308
00:14:25,208 --> 00:14:26,791
go home and get some rest.

309
00:14:27,750 --> 00:14:28,910
Wait for the school's notice.

310
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:30,500
Okay.

311
00:14:34,375 --> 00:14:35,375
Leave this place with me.

312
00:14:36,875 --> 00:14:37,875
Okay?

313
00:15:15,958 --> 00:15:17,278
You're just going to accept this?

314
00:15:34,916 --> 00:15:35,916
Say something!

315
00:15:37,166 --> 00:15:38,166
Bian Ye,

316
00:15:39,333 --> 00:15:41,250
being a school doctor
is just a part-time gig.

317
00:15:42,500 --> 00:15:44,083
My actual job is being a dentist.

318
00:15:45,958 --> 00:15:46,958
This clinic

319
00:15:47,458 --> 00:15:48,666
is where I truly work.

320
00:15:48,958 --> 00:15:49,958
That's still not fair!

321
00:15:50,250 --> 00:15:51,726
What right does she have
to expose your privacy

322
00:15:51,750 --> 00:15:52,750
in front of everyone?

323
00:16:06,375 --> 00:16:07,375
Because she hates me.

324
00:16:10,333 --> 00:16:11,333
Lin Xia's brother,

325
00:16:13,541 --> 00:16:14,541
Lin Fan,

326
00:16:21,833 --> 00:16:23,000
we used to be together.

327
00:16:25,083 --> 00:16:26,443
We ran away to the south together.

328
00:16:28,041 --> 00:16:29,041
Back then,

329
00:16:30,875 --> 00:16:33,708
I truly believed we could get
through anything together.

330
00:16:36,125 --> 00:16:37,125
Back then,

331
00:16:39,041 --> 00:16:40,333
Lin Xia actually supported us.

332
00:16:46,666 --> 00:16:47,666
So that person...

333
00:16:49,583 --> 00:16:50,583
was him.

334
00:16:56,291 --> 00:16:57,291
But

335
00:16:58,208 --> 00:16:59,583
didn't he abandon you?

336
00:17:00,875 --> 00:17:02,155
What gives Lin Xia the right?

337
00:17:04,666 --> 00:17:05,666
I lied to you.

338
00:17:10,250 --> 00:17:11,250
He

339
00:17:14,250 --> 00:17:15,416
died because of me.

340
00:17:19,083 --> 00:17:20,416
We were very happy once.

341
00:17:23,791 --> 00:17:25,291
We traveled to many places

342
00:17:27,291 --> 00:17:28,571
and did so many things together.

343
00:17:33,250 --> 00:17:34,250
But

344
00:17:39,833 --> 00:17:40,833
he still died.

345
00:17:43,500 --> 00:17:44,500
Three years ago,

346
00:17:45,916 --> 00:17:47,250
we went to the mountains of Tibet

347
00:17:47,750 --> 00:17:48,870
to volunteer as medical aid.

348
00:17:49,791 --> 00:17:50,791
That winter was freezing,

349
00:17:50,875 --> 00:17:52,595
and heavy snow blocked the mountain passes.

350
00:17:53,958 --> 00:17:55,791
A child in a village fell critically ill

351
00:17:55,916 --> 00:17:57,116
and needed medicine delivered.

352
00:18:01,083 --> 00:18:02,125
I insisted on going.

353
00:18:04,208 --> 00:18:05,291
He couldn't stop me,

354
00:18:07,041 --> 00:18:08,166
so he came with me.

355
00:18:10,458 --> 00:18:11,458
But then

356
00:18:12,041 --> 00:18:13,375
we got caught in an avalanche.

357
00:18:14,666 --> 00:18:16,666
I survived, but he...

358
00:18:18,125 --> 00:18:19,833
If I hadn't insisted on going,

359
00:18:20,916 --> 00:18:22,583
if I hadn't let him come with me,

360
00:18:23,375 --> 00:18:24,375
if only...

361
00:18:26,708 --> 00:18:27,958
Maybe he would have married,

362
00:18:28,500 --> 00:18:29,500
had kids,

363
00:18:31,041 --> 00:18:32,333
and lived a peaceful life.

364
00:18:40,500 --> 00:18:41,625
So Lin Xia is right

365
00:18:45,333 --> 00:18:46,333
to say those things.

366
00:18:48,583 --> 00:18:49,833
I took her brother away,

367
00:18:52,708 --> 00:18:53,875
and I failed to protect him.

368
00:18:55,416 --> 00:18:56,458
That wasn't your fault.

369
00:18:58,041 --> 00:18:59,601
Does it even matter whose fault it was?

370
00:19:02,250 --> 00:19:03,666
The point is, he's dead.

371
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:04,750
Because of me.

372
00:19:06,875 --> 00:19:08,750
So Lin Xia has every right to say that.

373
00:19:11,500 --> 00:19:12,620
I deserve to take the blame.

374
00:19:13,666 --> 00:19:14,666
No, you don't.

375
00:19:15,833 --> 00:19:17,291
Lin Fan's death was an accident.

376
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:21,400
You just fell in love with someone.

377
00:19:22,291 --> 00:19:22,833
Zhan Xu.

378
00:19:23,208 --> 00:19:24,333
Look at me, Zhan Xu.

379
00:19:25,041 --> 00:19:25,458
Zhan Xu,

380
00:19:25,708 --> 00:19:26,708
look at me!

381
00:19:27,416 --> 00:19:28,416
Lin Fan is dead.

382
00:19:28,833 --> 00:19:30,250
Are you going to die with him?

383
00:19:31,625 --> 00:19:33,125
Hiding yourself away in this dump,

384
00:19:34,083 --> 00:19:35,458
pretending to be "normal,"

385
00:19:35,958 --> 00:19:37,666
pretending none of it ever happened!

386
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:45,000
Bian Ye,

387
00:19:47,333 --> 00:19:48,333
you don't understand.

388
00:19:49,250 --> 00:19:50,250
You're right.

389
00:19:50,416 --> 00:19:51,416
I don't understand.

390
00:19:52,125 --> 00:19:53,976
I don't understand all
your complicated feelings.

391
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:54,708
But I do know

392
00:19:54,916 --> 00:19:55,916
that you have to move on.

393
00:19:56,458 --> 00:19:57,458
If you like men,

394
00:19:57,750 --> 00:19:59,041
then own it and love openly!

395
00:19:59,208 --> 00:20:00,875
If someone insults you, insult them back.

396
00:20:01,083 --> 00:20:02,708
If someone hits you, hit them back!

397
00:20:03,625 --> 00:20:04,625
Why put on a front?

398
00:20:04,833 --> 00:20:05,833
Why keep hiding?

399
00:20:06,208 --> 00:20:07,208
Just like right now.

400
00:20:07,250 --> 00:20:08,250
If you want to cry,

401
00:20:08,750 --> 00:20:09,750
don't hold it in.

402
00:20:09,875 --> 00:20:10,625
If you want to throw a fit,

403
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:11,750
then smash something!

404
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:16,000
Just like

405
00:20:21,500 --> 00:20:22,666
Just like right now.

406
00:20:23,250 --> 00:20:24,250
If you want something,

407
00:20:24,750 --> 00:20:25,750
just say it.

408
00:20:26,166 --> 00:20:27,166
Just do it.

409
00:20:27,625 --> 00:20:28,665
Don't keep bottling it up.

410
00:20:31,541 --> 00:20:32,541
Aren't you tired?

411
00:20:37,750 --> 00:20:38,750
Xu,

412
00:20:39,541 --> 00:20:40,541
Do you dare say

413
00:20:40,958 --> 00:20:42,583
you don't feel anything for me at all?

414
00:22:48,250 --> 00:22:49,650
We've known each other for so long.

415
00:22:49,958 --> 00:22:50,958
I'll take care of you.

416
00:22:52,166 --> 00:22:53,166
My brother's path...

417
00:22:53,666 --> 00:22:54,746
I won't walk down it again.

418
00:23:05,541 --> 00:23:06,541
Xu Yuan.

419
00:23:06,833 --> 00:23:07,833
Is that you, Xu Yuan?

420
00:23:45,125 --> 00:23:46,666
Xu Yuan, where are you?

421
00:24:05,756 --> 00:24:06,636
[Headline saying the Jinx
pushed someone for love]

422
00:24:06,708 --> 00:24:07,500
Zhan Xu,

423
00:24:07,708 --> 00:24:09,291
a gay man who likes men,

424
00:24:09,458 --> 00:24:11,166
stole my brother and got him killed.

425
00:24:11,583 --> 00:24:12,416
Because he's disgusting.

426
00:24:12,541 --> 00:24:13,541
Because he's filthy.

427
00:24:13,564 --> 00:24:14,764
[Message saying "Holy
shit" for some reason]

428
00:24:14,791 --> 00:24:15,809
Check the group chat, quick!

429
00:24:15,833 --> 00:24:16,833
This is huge gossip!

430
00:24:17,208 --> 00:24:18,648
Dr. Zhan, the school doctor, is gay!

431
00:24:18,750 --> 00:24:19,934
And he even got someone killed!

432
00:24:19,958 --> 00:24:22,125
That transfer student,
Zhan Wang, is his brother.

433
00:24:22,291 --> 00:24:23,208
Could he be gay too?

434
00:24:23,291 --> 00:24:25,083
A jinx and a gay guy's brother,

435
00:24:25,250 --> 00:24:26,267
and they're always glued to each other.

436
00:24:26,291 --> 00:24:27,291
Could they be...?

437
00:24:27,500 --> 00:24:29,220
It's not nice to talk about them like that.

438
00:24:29,244 --> 00:24:30,250
Damn, do you like him?

439
00:24:30,500 --> 00:24:31,833
What nonsense are you talking?

440
00:24:33,916 --> 00:24:35,333
Isn't this the jinx's shop?

441
00:24:35,916 --> 00:24:36,458
Stop talking.

442
00:24:36,625 --> 00:24:37,208
Don't look. Don't look.

443
00:24:37,333 --> 00:24:38,333
Hurry, let's go.

444
00:24:47,166 --> 00:24:48,875
Xu Yuan, why don't you just die?

445
00:24:51,583 --> 00:24:52,000
Bro.

446
00:24:52,458 --> 00:24:53,500
Did you see the video?

447
00:24:53,791 --> 00:24:55,031
What nonsense are they talking?

448
00:24:55,916 --> 00:24:57,625
Open the door! Don't scare me.

449
00:24:58,333 --> 00:24:59,333
I'm fine.

450
00:24:59,833 --> 00:25:00,625
I just overslept.

451
00:25:00,791 --> 00:25:01,791
I'll be right out.

452
00:25:02,291 --> 00:25:03,291
Are you really okay?

453
00:25:03,666 --> 00:25:04,851
What could possibly be wrong with me?

454
00:25:04,875 --> 00:25:06,515
Hurry up and pack your things for school.

455
00:25:23,125 --> 00:25:25,041
Xu Yuan, pick up the phone!

456
00:25:50,953 --> 00:25:56,166
[Signs saying "Get out of our school,"
"homosexual kill yourself," "AIDS" etc]

457
00:25:59,426 --> 00:26:02,026
["So nasty" "Being gay is a disease"]

458
00:26:03,819 --> 00:26:04,379
Fuck!

459
00:26:04,750 --> 00:26:05,375
Who did this?

460
00:26:05,625 --> 00:26:06,625
Show yourself!

461
00:26:06,875 --> 00:26:07,875
Don't be a coward!

462
00:26:08,541 --> 00:26:09,541
Stop shouting.

463
00:26:09,875 --> 00:26:10,875
You won't find them.

464
00:26:11,291 --> 00:26:12,851
Maybe you shouldn't go to school today.

465
00:26:13,458 --> 00:26:14,538
I'll ask for leave for you.

466
00:26:15,913 --> 00:26:16,433
Fuck!

467
00:26:16,875 --> 00:26:17,875
Because of this?

468
00:26:17,958 --> 00:26:18,958
I'm not afraid.

469
00:26:20,541 --> 00:26:21,541
There's no need.

470
00:26:22,583 --> 00:26:23,583
Just take a break first.

471
00:26:24,166 --> 00:26:25,291
Wait until this blows over.

472
00:26:26,333 --> 00:26:27,733
Didn't you want me to go to school?

473
00:26:27,875 --> 00:26:29,291
Fine, I'll go.

474
00:26:38,375 --> 00:26:39,375
He's here.

475
00:26:43,875 --> 00:26:44,500
That's him.

476
00:26:44,583 --> 00:26:45,708
He ruined Lin Xia's hand.

477
00:26:46,291 --> 00:26:47,351
And he still has the
nerve to show up at school.

478
00:26:47,375 --> 00:26:48,375
What a jinx.

479
00:26:48,416 --> 00:26:49,666
I heard he's gay too.

480
00:26:50,875 --> 00:26:51,583
I heard that too.

481
00:26:51,833 --> 00:26:52,833
Exactly.

482
00:27:01,625 --> 00:27:04,145
Remember your scooter?
You promised to pick me up for school,

483
00:27:05,375 --> 00:27:06,684
and I waited at the gate for ages.

484
00:27:06,708 --> 00:27:08,268
Breaking your promise means you owe me.

485
00:27:08,666 --> 00:27:09,666
How much?

486
00:27:11,166 --> 00:27:12,166
Xu Yuan.

487
00:27:12,916 --> 00:27:13,916
Look up.

488
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:21,000
What is this about?

489
00:27:22,583 --> 00:27:23,083
Are you avoiding me?

490
00:27:23,541 --> 00:27:24,541
Think whatever you want.

491
00:27:25,833 --> 00:27:28,166
The scooter key is in the ignition.

492
00:27:28,791 --> 00:27:29,791
Take it back.

493
00:27:31,208 --> 00:27:33,375
I won't be needing it
for deliveries anymore.

494
00:27:38,500 --> 00:27:39,500
Fine.

495
00:27:40,541 --> 00:27:41,621
I'll take the scooter back.

496
00:27:41,708 --> 00:27:42,767
But what about the tutoring

497
00:27:42,791 --> 00:27:43,791
and sparring fees?

498
00:27:44,208 --> 00:27:45,291
I can refund you the money.

499
00:27:46,291 --> 00:27:47,291
Or,

500
00:27:49,375 --> 00:27:50,935
you can find someone else to tutor you.

501
00:27:59,708 --> 00:28:01,500
Are you avoiding me because of those videos

502
00:28:01,791 --> 00:28:02,976
and what those idiots are saying,

503
00:28:03,000 --> 00:28:03,833
or is it because of Lin Xia?

504
00:28:03,916 --> 00:28:05,316
If something's wrong, just tell me.

505
00:28:07,291 --> 00:28:09,708
Lin Xia got hurt because of me.

506
00:28:12,083 --> 00:28:13,683
It's only natural that I care about her.

507
00:28:16,083 --> 00:28:18,123
Besides, you two have
known each other for so long,

508
00:28:18,291 --> 00:28:19,291
and you're even engaged.

509
00:28:20,375 --> 00:28:22,708
She needs you by her side right now.

510
00:28:24,375 --> 00:28:25,375
As for me,

511
00:28:25,625 --> 00:28:26,875
who am I to get in the way?

512
00:28:27,958 --> 00:28:28,958
Don't let me

513
00:28:29,541 --> 00:28:30,541
hold you two back.

514
00:28:31,166 --> 00:28:32,166
Fine.

515
00:28:33,500 --> 00:28:35,000
I'll do exactly as you say.

516
00:28:37,500 --> 00:28:38,500
I'll stay with her.

517
00:28:39,166 --> 00:28:40,166
I'll take care of her.

518
00:28:40,791 --> 00:28:42,591
I'll accept the relationship
I'm supposed to.

519
00:28:43,583 --> 00:28:45,208
And you can keep hiding in your shell,

520
00:28:45,750 --> 00:28:46,791
playing the jinx.
